  '019f79c8-9a00-7000-9000-000000000001'::uuid, '019f79c8-9a00-7000-8000-000000000001'::uuid, 1, 'quick-start', '快速开始', '从环境准备到第一个智能体，完成 AI Agent Platform 的最短上手路径。', '{"format":"safe-markdown-v1","source":"用一套最小流程验证平台、模型网关和知识库是否已经可以协同工作。\n\n:::callout{type=\"info\"}\n当前文档示例以本地 Docker\n环境为主，生产环境请结合企业网络、硬件和安全策略调整配置。\n:::\n\n## 上手路径\n\n:::steps\n\n### 准备环境\n\n准备 Docker、Docker Compose、PostgreSQL，并确认服务器可以访问所需镜像仓库。\n\n### 启动平台\n\n复制环境变量模板，填写数据库连接和公开访问地址，然后执行 `docker compose up -d`。\n\n### 创建第一个 Agent\n\n在 Agent Studio 中选择模型、工具和知识库，保存后用测试会话验证响应链路。\n\n:::\n\n## 接下来做什么\n\n:::cards\n- [部署指南](/docs/deployment)\n- [API 文档](/docs/api)\n- [常见问题 FAQ](/docs/faq)\n:::\n","checksum":"33ddd1cd30f25884725d4cdf0bd0aef0ff85742d0dc382a7e47495b2edf64838","navigation":{"label":"快速开始","code":"QUICK_START","position":10},"renderModel":{"version":1,"root":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"用一套最小流程验证平台、模型网关和知识库是否已经可以协同工作。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"document-callout","properties":{"dataCalloutType":"info"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当前文档示例以本地 Docker\n环境为主，生产环境请结合企业网络、硬件和安全策略调整配置。"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"doc-content-上手路径"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"上手路径"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"document-steps","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"doc-content-准备环境"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"准备环境"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"准备 Docker、Docker Compose、PostgreSQL，并确认服务器可以访问所需镜像仓库。"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"doc-content-启动平台"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"启动平台"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"复制环境变量模板，填写数据库连接和公开访问地址，然后执行 "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"docker compose up -d"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"doc-content-创建第一个-agent"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"创建第一个 Agent"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在 Agent Studio 中选择模型、工具和知识库，保存后用测试会话验证响应链路。"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"doc-content-接下来做什么"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"接下来做什么"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"document-cards","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"/docs/deployment"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"部署指南"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"/docs/api"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"API 文档"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"/docs/faq"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"常见问题 FAQ"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]}]}]},"toc":[{"id":"doc-content-上手路径","title":"上手路径","depth":2},{"id":"doc-content-准备环境","title":"准备环境","depth":3},{"id":"doc-content-启动平台","title":"启动平台","depth":3},{"id":"doc-content-创建第一个-agent","title":"创建第一个 Agent","depth":3},{"id":"doc-content-接下来做什么","title":"接下来做什么","depth":2}]}}'::jsonb, '2026-07-19T00:00:00.000Z'::timestamptz
